RegressionGraph.name: PredictedObserved
RegressionGraph.memo:
Note: If you have Observered data for some samplings but not others, then in the .out file (for the observations) you can use * or ? for those missing values instead of using 0
This allows you to tell the difference between data you did not collect, and data that actually had a value of 0
Data with a * or ? is not plotted on the graph (hence neither is its predicted value) whereas data with 0 is.

CropType.description: Select crop type to report variables for

script.text:
SimDay = 1
AccumPlantN = 0 AccumMineralisation = 0 AccumDenit = 0 AccumFert = 0 AccumLeach = 0 AccumDetach = 0 DeltaSoilOMN = 0 DeltaSurfaceOMN = 0 DeltaSoilMineralN = 0
AccumEO = 0 AccumEP = 0 AccumES = 0 AccumDrainage = 0 AccumRunoff = 0 AccumOutflowLat = 0 AccumIrrigation = 0 AccumRainfall = 0 SoilWaterDeficit = 0
LeafLiveNConc3 = 0 LeafDeadNConc3 = 0 StemLiveNConc3 = 0 TuberLiveNConc3 = 0
AccumTtemerg = 0
leavesPerStem = 0

if simday = 1 then InitialSoilOMN = biom_n() + fom_n() + hum_n() InitialSurfaceOMN = surfaceom_n InitialMineralN = no3() + nh4() + urea() endif
!!!!!! Nitrogen balance components !!!!!! !!!!!!^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^!!!!!! AccumPlantN = (0 - [CropType].LeafLiveN2 - [CropType].LeafDeadN2 - [CropType].StemLiveN - [CropType].stemdeadn - [CropType].TuberLiveN - [CropType].tuberdeadN ) * 10 !+ [CropType].RootLiveN + [CropType].RootDeadN AccumMineralisation = AccumMineralisation + dlt_n_min() + dlt_n_min_res() AccumDenit = AccumDenit - dnit() AccumFert = AccumFert + fertiliser AccumLeach = AccumLeach - leach_urea - leach_no3 - leach_nh4 AccumDetach = 0 !plant2 doesn't detach yet DeltaSoilOMN = (biom_n() + fom_n() + hum_n()) - InitialSoilOMN DeltaSurfaceOMN = surfaceom_n - InitialSurfaceOMN DeltaSoilMineralN = (no3() + nh4() + urea()) - InitialMineralN
!!!!!! Water balance components !!!!!! !!!!!!^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^!!!!!! AccumEO = AccumEO - eo AccumEP = AccumEP - [CropType].LeafTranspiration AccumES = AccumES - es AccumDrainage = AccumDrainage - drain AccumRunoff = AccumRunoff - runoff AccumOutflowLat = AccumOutflowLat - outflow_lat() AccumIrrigation = AccumIrrigation + Irrigation AccumRainfall = Accumrainfall + rain SoilWaterDeficit = sw_dep() - dul_dep()
!!!!!! Organ N % !!!!!! !!!!!!^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^!!!!!! !FIXME These variables are created because those reported by biomass object only have 2dp if [CropType].LeafLiveWt2 > 0 then LeafLiveNConc3 = ([CropType].LeafLiveN2/[CropType].LeafLiveWt2) endif if [CropType].LeafDeadWt2 > 0 then LeafDeadNConc3 = ([CropType].LeafDeadN2/[CropType].LeafDeadWt2) endif if [CropType].tuberlivewt > 0 then TuberLiveNConc3 = ([CropType].tuberliveN/[CropType].tuberlivewt) endif if [CropType].stemlivewt > 0 then StemLiveNConc3 = ([CropType].stemliveN/[CropType].stemlivewt) endif
!!!!!! Thermal time calculation !!!!!! !!!!!! ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ !!!!!! If [CropType].StageCodeValue >= 3 Then AccumTtemerg = AccumTtemerg + [CropType].PhenologyThermalTimeValue Endif
leavesPerStem = [croptype].leaftotalno / 3
if SimDay = 1 then SimDay = 2 Else SimDay = 2 endif
